WORLD POPULATION<br />
- Ancient Port Warehouse - It is no longer possible to summon a boat within the port of Innovus.<br />
- Ancient Port Warehouse - Spawnable bosses in APW now drop Hoptonian Ore.<br />
- Ancient Port Warehouse - The Core Processor will now mitigate spell damage as it was intended to do.<br />
