<br />
8. Give us some better buffs, i hate bringing absolutely nothing beneficial to groups/raids. See invis and resists - loooool, give us some damage wards that are single target, and for spell damage/melee damage (1k damage seems fine), or at least a 50% spell mitigation buff<br />
<br />
