                  ok, if a developer wants to give me a call on Skype, i can sit down and explain in detail all of the issues with Sorcs in PVE and PVP. I played a Wiz in EQ, and know the balancement issues pretty well. PM me, in any way, i can write a nice summary of sorc class if asked.<br />
<br />
Now wanna say a few good things about sorcs )<br />
<br />
My pvp style SOLO:<br />
<br />
1. Opener - flame sprear from about 30m, come in and cast fire ball ASAP, follow by char. THrow in crit/amplifying if they are up, mine are almost always down<br />
<br />
2. Create a finisher macro (fire finisher 1/ fire finisher 2/ mimic)<br />
<br />
3. Get panther mask, it stacks with quicksilver ring. get avarem's messenger bag as well if u can. My self buffed unmounted speed is about 165% or so, pretty nice if you ask me. Learn to quickly turn in off to get on horse/flying mount.<br />
<br />
4. Always look for resist buffs on pvp targets, use tab for fast switch between them and select targets with less resists.<br />
<br />
4. Forget about infamy, the less you pay attention to it, the higher it will go. I stopped checking mine, and after a while saw it at 3k once, up from 1k couple of hours earlier )<br />
<br />
5. Learn to juke, joust, hide, use LoS to evade spells/range attacks/ melee. Takes a while to learn, but thats a difference between a good sorc and a pve crying baby sorc<br />
<br />
6. Get maximum mount speed, mine is 315%, i have several APW items (saddlebags - 10%, ironshoes  - 50%, etc etc)<br />
<br />
7. STAY INVISED ALL THE TIME, drop it only to finish/kill people. Sorc invis is one of the best in game FYU<br />
<br />
8. Items. U will need a lot of it. Get awareness robe vs rogues and rangers (gives something like +300 awareness or so). JohnAlex told me of an 8sec silence melee staff from Xennu, only needs 50 shards, that might be nice too. Need to get it myself and try out.<br />
<br />
9. Dont ever cry in /ooc about sorcs being gimp, or I come and camp you off the server. /serious<br />
<br />
8. Help out our brother psyonisists as much as you can, group with them and give them kills/infamy. They were shitted upon much more than us, help them out when you see them.<br />
<br />
9. SOrcs is a 100% offensive class, remember it. Its either your are attacking, or you die.<br />
<br />
10. Get 50, give your infamy that you have accumulated to an alt or friend, and go on a dying streek for a few weeks to learn what other classes can do to you. Dont worry about gear, its not that imporant for our class at all.<br />
<br />
11. Send a tell to Agrul on Sartok, i ll help you our with gear/money/advice if you decide to start on a PVP server. Just dont bring that carebear attitude please, its dog eat dog out here.<br />
<br />
12. Have fun with your sorc, if you are having problems, play another class, they are just as much fun. <br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
4. <br />
<br />
4.
                  
